### TESTES DE VALIDAÇÃO (devem retornar erro)
### ============================================

### Erro: Valor negativo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": -50.00,
  "type": "credit",
  "status": "completed",
  "userId": "substitua-por-um-id-valido"
}

### Erro: Tipo inválido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "type": "invalid_type",
  "status": "completed",
  "userId": "substitua-por-um-id-valido"
}

### Erro: Status inválido
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transactions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "type": "credit",
  "status": "invalid_status",
  "userId": "substitua-por-um-id-valido"
}

